name: Asparagus Canyon
description:
Introduction

A scenic adventure into West Clear Creek.

Approach

Walk into obvious drainage.

Descent

Small cave.

Downclimb through rabbit hole or go way around LDC.

R1: 30' optional or downclimb ledges center of canyon.

R2: 40' optional or downclimb LDC then down crack.

Boulder hop to confluence with WCC.

Exit

Exit up same way you came down.

Red tape

Beta sites

Trip reports and media
